<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201130/78f6b56c3235436b9145d49dd3ad83f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>5.办公区域。办公室员工轮流分批上班，上班时戴口罩，隔板阻挡交流，每天进行热感检测。</strong> </p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20201130/634ae0976828408b8714345469752b61.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
